      "content": "I see. Some people online claim that these studies actually show a clear hierarchy or a predictable ranking between certain groups. If you look at the more controversial literature, specifically works that move beyond just \"heritability\" and actually discuss specific racial groups, what are the core findings or conclusions they present regarding which groups tend to score higher or lower? I'm trying to understand the specific data points that drive these debates.",
